<p>Leffel, T., Xiang, M., &amp; Kennedy, C. (2016). Imprecision is pragmatic: Evidence from referential processing. Semantics and Linguistic Theory, 26, 836-854.</p>

<p>Qing, C., Lassiter, D., &amp; Degen, J. (2018). What do eye movements in the visual world reflect? A case study from adjectives. Cognitive Science.</p>
